cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.NE 

This paper is about image restoration using a novel multi-level wavelet CNN model. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of wavelet transform, which falls under the sub-category cs.MM (Mathematical Methods). The model architecture and optimization techniques used in the paper also suggest the possibility of it belonging to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of subsampling and reconstruction techniques, which fall under the sub-categories cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), respectively.
